Job Title: Software Engineer

We lookin' for a skilled Software Engineer to join our team.  The ideal candidate gotta got a strong background in software development, knowin'  Java, C++, or Python.  Responsibilities include designin', codin', testin', and debugg'n software; integratin' systems and software; and makin' sure everything works right.  You need a Computer Science degree or somethin' similar, and at least two years experience doin' this kinda work.  You gotta be good at solvin' problems and workin' alone or on a team. Knowin' Agile and databases is a plus.  The Software Engineer reports to the IT Manager and works with the team to make top-notch software.
